 Potter hascome a long wayfrom the athletewho morosely sipped cocktailsfrom a coconut on the Copacabana eight years ago.\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 493, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beth Potter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beth_Potter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletewho\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"a coconut\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"the Copacabana\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her career was at an inflection point after a distant 38th-place finish in the 10,000m at the RioOlympicsbut a chance meeting in McDonald's and aswitch of sports was rewardedatParis 2024with women'striathlonbronze.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her career\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 629}, {\"ngram\": \"an inflection point\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"a distant 38th-place finish\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10,000m\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"the RioOlympicsbut\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"McDonald\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"aswitch\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 780}, {\"ngram\": \"rewardedatParis\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"2024with\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 809}, {\"ngram\": \"women'striathlonbronze\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potterwon the test event here last yearand the world title but this season has failed to make the top step of the podium at the global level, claiming she wasarriving in Parisflying under the radar.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the test event\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"this season\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"the top step\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 941}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"the global level\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"the radar\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her tactics were clear: stay in contention through the swim and stay out of trouble on the bike, where greasy cobbled sections were treacherous after heavy overnight rain.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her tactics\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"contention\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"trouble\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"greasy cobbled sections\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"heavy overnight rain\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then she could strike on the run, where, on her day, she's the strongest athlete in the field.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the run\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"her day\", \"from\": 1252, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"the strongest athlete\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she did not count on France's Cassandre Beaugrand who, roared on by a sea of French tricolours along this made-for-Instagram course, proved just too strong.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8927329469966409, \"rank\": 0.07844466939632197, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\