o\": 2054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a wall of noise out there, there was not one part of that course that was quiet.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wall\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2069}, {\"ngram\": \"noise\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2078}, {\"ngram\": \"one part\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2112}, {\"ngram\": \"that course\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2127}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have come a long way in eight years and I really feel like I did this for me and for those who believed in what I was doing switching sports.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight years\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Brownlees have been a massive part of my journey.\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2345, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Brownlees\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive part\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are the reason I moved to the triathlon.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"the triathlon\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I train with Alistair day in, day out, and he's such a big part of my story.\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Alistair day\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2417}, {\"ngram\": \"such a big part\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2455}, {\"ngram\": \"my story\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I moved in with Jonny when I first moved to Leeds too.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"score\": 0.9999794127379656, \"rank\": 2.0500052220828034e-05, \"text\": \"Leeds\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jonny\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are always the first to message me before and after races and it means so much to know that I have the support of them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The water quality in the Seinehas been the talking point of recent days, despite the high-profile efforts of French authorities to clean it up at a reported cost of \\u00a31bn.\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2762, \"end\": 2768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8521679032154684, \"rank\": 0.14957413415288895, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The water quality\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seinehas\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2686}, {\"ngram\": \"the talking point\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"recent days\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"the high-profile efforts\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"a reported cost\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a31bn\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's race was already delayed 24 hours and Potter and teammates Georgia Taylor-Brown, who finished sixth, and Kate Waugh went to bed last night not knowing whether they'd race in the morning.\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2894, \"end\": 2914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Taylor-Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Georgia Taylor-Br