s and probiotics and lined her stomach with Peptobismol; she'd barely caught her breath before she was gurgling mouthwash.\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Taylor-Brown\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"a cocktail\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"prebiotics\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"probiotics\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3629}, {\"ngram\": \"her stomach\", \"from\": 3640, \"to\": 3651}, {\"ngram\": \"Peptobismol\", \"from\": 3657, \"to\": 3668}, {\"ngram\": \"her breath\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3700}, {\"ngram\": \"mouthwash\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3734}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France and Great Britain look the ones to beat in the team event, with Taylor-Brown and Yee likely to be the only returning members of the gold medal-winning quartet from Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3737, \"to\": 3914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3737, \"end\": 3743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8927329469966409, \"rank\": 0.07844466939632197, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3748, \"end\": 3761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9903674393730247, \"rank\": 0.006903087420684043, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3908, \"end\": 3913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9460244113086146, \"rank\": 0.05600354393889457, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ones\", \"from\": 3767, \"to\": 3775}, {\"ngram\": \"the team event\", \"from\": 3